When you think of Gula, you think of its lush, green land!
Furniture made from Gulan wood makes
the perfect souvenir!

rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
It's wonderful, isn't it!
This city of Torigoth has an even richer
supply of trees than other Gulan cities.

rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
The quality of our specialty products is different
from other Gulan cities. After all, it's handmade! Handmade!

rows.label: tlk41400021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Once you pick it up, you're sure to be
captivated!
